{"tid":765872,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：西環 Thai Ros Zab","createTime":"2018-08-03T06:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T10:33:00.000Z","uid":181719,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f87cd147eb79ae286bb43c7ab21f270b729bcce2","tid":765872,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"一般食泰菜都係去九龍城架啦，但自從開始寫食評之後，我反而多咗試其他地方嘅泰菜，因為九龍城太出名唔駛我介紹啦。咁有一次食完南北美食館，經過發現呢間泰國菜，就搵晚去咗試。似乎間間泰菜都係要食個泰字的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/143212_883ed5ee32906dd3ad23724b16f4ba63.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F143212_883ed5ee32906dd3ad23724b16f4ba63.jpeg&h=fc2278a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/143212_625aa6af6c7004d25d7f88e01ea5beea.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F143212_625aa6af6c7004d25d7f88e01ea5beea.jpeg&h=fba8321a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去果晚又係冇乜人，嗌咗泰式炒粉絲、泰式炒通菜同埋好唔泰式嘅蜜糖焗排骨，200蚊埋單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炒粉絲同通菜基本上都係夠鑊氣，夠味，唔好炒燶，咁就已經好好食，呢度係絕對做到有餘嘅，碟粉絲配料仲好豐富添，算好抵食。唯一缺點係叫得泰式但係好唔夠辣，我食開譚仔3小架啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/143228_568aaea6aed01f05b36e4cde500cc8e9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F143228_568aaea6aed01f05b36e4cde500cc8e9.jpeg&h=cbfbb463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/143229_9e25ee82d706f770dd62980a9632b23e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F143229_9e25ee82d706f770dd62980a9632b23e.jpeg&h=91f28a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於好唔泰式嘅蜜糖焗排骨，味道就不過不失啦，可能自己特別中意呢種先甜後咸嘅味道，所以對呢味餸會加咗分。不過佢啲豬肉略嫌不夠咬口，如果嚼感可以再彈牙啲就perfect喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/143239_4604c475577432b68a0c463adfb3314c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F143239_4604c475577432b68a0c463adfb3314c.jpeg&h=a8565c0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59d4d53d58b637789a0dd6968a6d2932a732045a","tid":765872,"uid":91834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"呢間我以前返工lunch會食<br />\n覺得唔錯"},{"pid":"8f0331500df2c2a4d43de00942a6247c48e2e713","tid":765872,"uid":48085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"呢間堅正"},{"pid":"ff9f0c1d80de14981abafdcff87d04932e2abf28","tid":765872,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d4d53d58b637789a0dd6968a6d2932a732045a","tid":765872,"uid":91834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"呢間我以前返工lunch會食<br />\n覺得唔錯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"果頭真係太多好野食，德記，加記，南北......"},{"pid":"b6fec4d54757614cd402274b21a78b4271ef1960","tid":765872,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f0331500df2c2a4d43de00942a6247c48e2e713","tid":765872,"uid":48085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"呢間堅正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a7ba1bf9a63026151a280cf54583200c0ce1da","tid":765872,"uid":2545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff9f0c1d80de14981abafdcff87d04932e2abf28","tid":765872,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d4d53d58b637789a0dd6968a6d2932a732045a","tid":765872,"uid":91834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1